---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About" description="About Scribe - Singapore Parliament proceedings made accessible">
  <h1 class="mb-6 text-3xl font-bold text-zinc-900">
    About Scribe
  </h1>

  <div class="prose prose-zinc max-w-none">
    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-zinc-900 mb-4">What is Scribe?</h2>
      <p class="text-zinc-600 mb-4">
        Scribe is a project to make Singapore Parliament proceedings more accessible and searchable.
        It processes the official Hansard records and presents them in a user-friendly format, making
        it easier to explore parliamentary questions, bills, motions, and member activities.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-zinc-900 mb-4">Data Sources</h2>
      <p class="text-zinc-600 mb-4">
        All data is sourced from the official Singapore Parliament Hansard, available at
        <a
          href="https://www.parliament.gov.sg/parliamentary-business/hansard"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="text-blue-600 hover:underline"
        >
          parliament.gov.sg
        </a>.
      </p>
      <p class="text-zinc-600 mb-4">
        The Hansard is the official record of parliamentary debates and includes:
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-zinc-600 mb-4 space-y-1">
        <li>Questions and answers (oral and written)</li>
        <li>Bill readings and debates</li>
        <li>Motions and ministerial statements</li>
        <li>Member attendance records</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-zinc-900 mb-4">AI Summaries</h2>
      <p class="text-zinc-600 mb-4">
        Some content includes AI-generated summaries to help readers quickly understand the key
        points of parliamentary proceedings. These summaries are provided for convenience and
        should not be considered official records. Always refer to the original Hansard for
        authoritative information.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-zinc-900 mb-4">Disclaimer</h2>
      <p class="text-zinc-600 mb-4">
        This is an unofficial project and is not affiliated with the Singapore Parliament or
        the Government of Singapore. While we strive for accuracy, the official Hansard
        should be consulted for authoritative records.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-zinc-900 mb-4">Links</h2>
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-zinc-600 space-y-2">
        <li>
          <a
            href="https://www.parliament.gov.sg/"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="text-blue-600 hover:underline"
          >
            Singapore Parliament Official Website
          </a>
        </li>
        <li>
          <a
            href="https://www.parliament.gov.sg/parliamentary-business/hansard"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="text-blue-600 hover:underline"
          >
            Official Hansard Records
          </a>
        </li>
        <li>
          <a
            href="https://www.parliament.gov.sg/parliamentary-business/order-paper"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="text-blue-600 hover:underline"
          >
            Order Paper (Parliament Agenda)
          </a>
        </li>
        <li>
          <a
            href="https://www.youtube.com/@SingaporeMDDI/streams"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="text-blue-600 hover:underline"
          >
            Parliament Live Streams (MDDI YouTube)
          </a>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </section>
  </div>
</Layout>
